(2+\cot\theta)^2=\csc^2\theta
\implies 4+x^2+4x=x^2+1
\implies 4x=-3\implies x=-3/4\implies \tan\theta=-4/3\implies \theta=\pi-\arctan(4/3),2\pi-\arctan(4/3)
